Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼讓我擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露海露米娜..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我看著就多吃甜的東西可不.....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我能擁抱你嗎？
