Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..不告訴你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..等等我啊 夏娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵..不等！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎幺這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在御崎市的調理師加姆西
